00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:36,958
pemainnya Barbara Streisand, aku...

281
00:28:37,125 --> 00:28:38,393
Entahlah. Aku menyukainya dan...

282
00:28:38,417 --> 00:28:39,917
- Benarkah?
- Ya.

